<H1>Changing your environment: Bourne shell</H1>

<P>At login the Bourne shell reads the initialisation files
<SAMP>/etc/profile</SAMP> and <SAMP>$HOME/.profile</SAMP>. You cannot
change the content of <SAMP>/etc/profile</SAMP>, but you have permission
to edit the contents of <SAMP>.profile</SAMP>, which is in your home
directory and is owned by you.</P>

